While creating custom fields in JIRA, the user should provide an option of whether the field values should be copied or not while cloning of issues.

Currently all the issue fields are cloned, this might cause data inconsistency. With custom fields that are important for our integration scenarios to other systems, we need to control the cloning procedure, as this leads to inconsistencies in Jira and the integrated system. E.g. : One of the user has cloned an issue and the test cases (as part of our integration to another system ) are also cloned but the test case doesn’t have the reference to the cloned issue.
A solution would be to give custom fields the option to de part of the cloning (default) or to be handled via a post function.

